Description_lang: Gain access to Marasmius's mushroom network, allowing you to travel to fae rings throughout Ardenweald.

description_blz.en_US: Gain access to Marasmius's mushroom network, allowing you to travel to fae rings throughout Ardenweald.
description_blz.es_MX: Obtienes acceso a la red de champiñones de Marasmius y puedes viajar a los anillos feéricos de Ardenweald.
description_blz.pt_BR: Obtém acesso à rede de cogumelos de Marasmius, podendo viajar pelos círculos feérios espalhados por Ardena.
description_blz.de_DE: Verschafft Euch Zugang zu Marasmius' Pilznetzwerk, sodass Ihr zu Faeringen überall im Ardenwald reisen könnt.
description_blz.en_GB: Gain access to Marasmius's mushroom network, allowing you to travel to fae rings throughout Ardenweald.
description_blz.es_ES: Obtienes acceso a la red de champiñones de Marasmius, lo que te permite viajar por los anillos de sílfides a lo largo de Ardenweald.
description_blz.fr_FR: Vous accédez au réseau mycélien de Marasmius, ce qui vous permet de voyager en empruntant les cercles des Faë de Sylvarden.
description_blz.it_IT: Fornisce accesso alla rete fungina di Marasmio, permettendoti di viaggiare verso gli anelli dei Silfi di tutta Selvarden.
description_blz.ru_RU: Дает доступ к грибной сети Чесночника, которая позволяет путешествовать по волшебным кольцам в Арденвельде.
description_blz.ko_KR: 마라스미우스의 버섯 연결망을 이용할 수 있게 됩니다. 몽환숲 전역에 자리한 페이 고리로 이동이 가능합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 得以使用瑪拉茲莫斯的蘑菇網路，使你可以前往亞登曠野各地的妖精之環。
description_blz.zh_CN: 可以进入玛拉斯缪斯的蘑网，让你在炽蓝仙野的蘑网之间旅行。
